high_descs: Turn around and walk to the end of the room, then turn to your left and go to the small counter, between the stove and the wall.
Pick up the apple, behind the coffee cup, on the counter.
Turn to your left and walk towards the brick wall across from you until you reach the marble sink, on your right.
Place the apple in the back, left corner of the sink, turn the water on, rinse the apple off, turn the water off, and remove the apple from the sink.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, then turn to the end of the wooden table, on your right.
Place the apple between the two spoons on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn right then head to the right side of the stove counter
Pick up the apple on the counter
Turn left and head to the sink
Put the apple in the sink and rinse it
Turn around to your right then walk forward face the table on your right
Put the apple on the table beside the spoon
anns.task_desc: Put the clean apple on the table

high_descs: Turn to the right and take two steps, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn left.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right.
Put the apple in the sink, turn on the faucet for three seconds, then turn off the water and pick up the apple.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right to face the table.
Put the apple down to the right of the spoon.
